  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para> 
<list>
<item>Describe the Standard Model in terms of the four fundamental forces and exchange particles</item>
<item>Draw a Feynman diagram for a simple particle interaction</item>
<item>Use Heisenberg’s uncertainty principle to determine the range of forces described by the Standard Model</item>
<item>Explain the rationale behind grand unification theories</item></list></md:abstract>
